36:09.778 --> 36:11.979
'cause I don't know what
was going on with me.

36:12.014 --> 36:13.681
He told me...

36:13.699 --> 36:17.969
"can't live under my roof
while you figure it out."

36:22.808 --> 36:25.176
So what'd you do then?

36:25.210 --> 36:28.579
Oh, I hitched a ride to Abilene, got a job,

36:28.614 --> 36:32.733
